        "body": "Supersedes #1728 while preserving its contributor commits and attribution.\n\nOriginal implementation by @LeoLin990405 in #1728.\n\n## Summary\n- add Sakana AI as a manual-cookie usage provider\n- parse five-hour and weekly quota windows from the billing page\n- wire provider metadata, settings, CLI support, icons, docs, and tests\n\n## Maintainer hardening\n- isolate the fetcher in an ephemeral cookie-free session\n- reject cross-origin or non-HTTPS redirects\n- avoid leaking private response bodies in errors\n- pin the parser language and reject impossible usage percentages\n\n## Validation\n- repository formatting and lint checks pass\n- Sakana focused suite passes all 9 tests\n- full required CI must pass before merge",
